# yeti Theme Demo
Output examples/svgs/themes/yeti.svg

Set Theme yeti
Set Template macos
Set Title "yeti"
Set FontSize 14

Type "echo 'Welcome to the yeti theme!'"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "echo 'This is how your terminal looks.'"
Sleep 200ms
Left 22
Shift+Right 3
Sleep 400ms
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1s
